cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

This paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for estimating 3D human pose from 2D images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper involves the use of deep learning models and optimization techniques, which are commonly used in the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with 3D graphics and geometry, which are relevant to the sub-category of cs.GR (Graphics). Finally, the paper involves the use of cameras and image processing techniques, which are relevant to the sub-category of cs.MM (Multimedia).
